name: Kitsune Pt.2
description:
1919x2849px

Nikko, Japan

#35mm film, shot on Minolta 700si. This shot was taken in a ryokan in the forest of Nikko. People say that many spirits live in these woods and while i did not experience anything supernatural, the mood and atmosphere in the couple of days i spent up there was truly magical. The name Kitsune is referred to the fox in Japanese mythology.
